meanings.definition: A member of the Entocyematidae family of ostracods (seed shrimp) that are ectosymbionts or parasites on freshwater crayfish.
meanings.english_definition: A member of the Entocyematidae family of ostracods (seed shrimp) that are ectosymbionts or parasites on freshwater crayfish.

examples.sentence: The entocyemate was found attached to the gills of the crayfish.
examples.translation: そのentocyemateは、ザリガニのエラに付着しているのが見つかりました。
